0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"為警界清理門戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440753cea4442ec58c501a767e944f13434fd4c5","tid":847464,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"你唔叫我張sir呀？仲叫我張家輝呀？<br />\n張家輝tone"},{"pid":"a29dc7bb869aecf6903438edc74e093173055440","tid":847464,"uid":3656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"最諷刺係，張家輝未做演員前真係做警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}